description:
It's routine for the rich to dodge tax by hiding it offshore. But how much of their wealth are they hiding illegally? Tim Phillips talks to Annette Alstadsæter of the Norwegian University of Life Sciences about how she and her colleagues used whistleblower data to discover the extent of tax evasion by the ultra-rich.&#13;
&#13;
[Read about their research on VoxEU](https://voxeu.org/article/tax-evasion-and-inequality).

